Minus the trouble I had during shipping, it was all sorted it out and in the end I received a beautiful QUALITY product with a gorgeous gift box. And it appears that multiple customers of theirs will second my experience with their quality standard.
the watch is beautiful.

review_title: the best part of this watch is
review_content: the best part of this watch is..its simple and classy but what is more awesome about this is you can change the battery easily and also change the band with real leather and also, if the glass cracks, you can change it. very fixable.

I received this watch today in the mail after ordering it just a few days ago. It is exactly what I was looking for. I love the detailing in the hands and the way it is designed to clasp is so unique! It fits me perfectly because of how many places there are to adjust it. I usually have trouble with watches because my wrist is so small that they slide around and annoy me...with this watch I can adjust it down to the perfect size. Beautifully crafted.
i love it, my friends love it, its super cool.

It is a cheap watch but function well so far. I read the reviews before I bought it. Personally, I felt the watch face is too shining and too big for my wrist. All in all, I do not feel that it has an amazing look as I read from other reviews but so far it does the work.

I love love love this watch! I wear it everyday. I get a lot of components on it. I love the old fashioned style way of securing it. My only complaint is that if I am doing a lot of vigorous activity with my hands, one side of the watch will kinda pop off the strap. It's a simple fix, similar to putting a toilet paper roll back on. Other than that, it has been great.
The band is a little awkward and takes some getting used to. But nice watch--really like it
Very cute and stylish.
Bought 3 of these watches, one for myself and for my friends and I Love it very much, but due to the leather the band is kind of hard to adjust; but do-able.
Love it! Exactly like picture, good material, i love this store

I spent a lot of time reading through reviews of suitcase covers. These stretchable covers are a fairly new product because even though I travel a lot, I have yet to see one on the carousel. The airlines ruined 2 of my suitcases recently and I found these stretchy covers while I was searching for some kind of plastic wrap to wrap the suitcase in. It fits my carry-on (the one I check in) perfectly and the bright colors really stand out. I chose this model because it has a zipper closure rather than velcro, and I'm so happy I did.

review_title: great way to protect hardsided luggage from damage
review_content: I'm very happy with this purchase (and have actually bought another one for a different size suitcase).
Very good product, the best thing is they have a zipper below instead of velcro.
Will order again in the future for future travels.
the quality of this cover is considerably better than the other more expensive one
My mom travels a lot and ordered this for her bag and absolutely loves it! uses it everytime to recognize it easily and also helps with preventing someone from opening it through the zipper.
Can't miss my luggage!

review_title: Very surprised by how nice the material is
review_content: Recieved the first cover just a couple days after ordering and my second one should arrive today. Very surprised by how nice the material is. They print is sooooo CUTE! I'll be able to spot it instantly now.

review_title: Fit fine. My only bad was that it is side ...
review_content: Fit fine. My only bad was that it is side specific but I work around that. Cover works great and fits great
I love this covet bougt for my husbands bag. Hopefully he will see it clealy on the belt.
